headline: HSBC Trims AMD Target Amid Revised Pricing Assumptions
summary: Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. (NASDAQ:AMD) is one of the AI Stocks on Wall Street’s Radar. On September 9, HSBC analyst Frank Lee lowered the price target on the stock to $185.00 (from $200.00) while maintaining a Buy rating. The lower price target comes after the firm revised its assumptions regarding AMD’s MI355 chip average selling price […]
